title: Lunchbox Spills The Tea On Eddie + Amy Has An Awkward Moment At The Doctor
itunes:title: Lunchbox Spills The Tea On Eddie + Amy Has An Awkward Moment At The Doctor
description:
Lunchbox shares some dirt on what Eddie’s been doing when Bobby is on the road. Lady Antebellum stops by to talk about their new single “What If I Never Get Over You,” and they also compete against the show in a game of Family Feud. Also, Amy has an awkward moment during her kids’ recent check-up appointment.
